Welcome to Riff! Feel free to look around and let me know if you have any questions or concerns
What kind of features are there in Riff?

That's a good question, our application has many user friendly features that is similar to Discord, Slack, and AOL Chat. We offer security through user authentification, the ability to create, modify, and join various servers and channels that you can post in and meet like minded individuals, as well as instant direct messaging.
Wow, that's amazing! Discord is one of the most popular apps and this feels so similar to it!
It feels like the developers put in a lot of effort and reallty knew what they were doing!
Thank you for your kind words, we have a really good team of developers working on the application.
Are there any servers that I am not allowed in?

Yes, there are public servers that anybody can access like the WelcomeToRiff server. I have granted you access to several of the private servers like RFP2210, AmongUs, and Minecraft, so that you can take a look around.
Thank you for your help! I think I should be able to navigate my way around from here
No problem, I hope you enjoy the application and you are welcome to leave any feedback you might have.
